Enhance your scheduling experience with the CompanyOS Chrome Extension! This powerful tool lets meeting organizers seamlessly link their CompanyOS meetings to Google Calendar events, ensuring all participants are promptly notified and well-prepared for the upcoming discussion. Additionally, the extension enables easy access to CompanyOS meetings directly from the user-friendly Google Calendar interface. Take advantage of the following features:

• Link your CompanyOS meeting to calendar events
• Promptly remind meeting participants to prepare for the upcoming meeting
• Seamlessly navigate to your CompanyOS meeting via Google Calendar's intuitive UI.
